00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:05,680
just to get the array from him.

295
00:18:07,360 --> 00:18:08,620
That's not fair to say.

296
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:10,500
After all these years,

297
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:11,770
without any backup,

298
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:14,160
I've done pretty well for myself.

299
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,760
I could have easily killed him,

300
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:16,560
couldn't I?

301
00:18:18,640 --> 00:18:19,720
Don't be so tense.

302
00:18:20,520 --> 00:18:22,480
Since I've brought him to you,

303
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:25,370
I won't do anything more to him.

304
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:28,380
Actually, I quite admire him.

305
00:18:29,080 --> 00:18:30,210
His faith is strong,

306
00:18:30,520 --> 00:18:31,980
his position unwavering.

307
00:18:33,080 --> 00:18:34,680
No matter how I tortured him,

308
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:37,560
I couldn't make him talk.

309
00:18:54,360 --> 00:18:55,620
You've met the person.

310
00:18:56,880 --> 00:18:58,080
What about the array?

311
00:18:58,400 --> 00:18:59,480
Can you tell me now?

312
00:18:59,600 --> 00:19:00,400
No.

313
00:19:03,840 --> 00:19:05,440
Fu Gang must return to China.

314
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,930
I need you to guarantee his safety.

315
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:10,810
Take him to Dongzhou City Police Station.

316
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:13,930
Then I'll tell you about the array.

317
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:14,800
Otherwise,

318
00:19:15,560 --> 00:19:16,360
no deal.

319
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:19,480
To prevent you from taking him somewhere

320
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:21,080
and quietly disposing of him.

321
00:19:21,080 --> 00:19:22,320
I want a video call.

322
00:19:23,320 --> 00:19:25,560
