323
00:19:25,560 --> 00:19:28,960
Standing safely at the entrance of Dongzhou Police Station.

324
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,130
What I promised you,

325
00:19:35,360 --> 00:19:36,360
I've done it all.

326
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:38,120
So where's my array?

327
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:39,220
Listen carefully.

328
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,060
The sequence is...

329
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:45,280
You suspect there's something fishy about Chi Xia being wanted by the police?

330
00:19:45,280 --> 00:19:47,400
Even if this falls into the hands of the police,

331
00:19:47,400 --> 00:19:48,600
what good would it do?

332
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:49,720
The password

333
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:50,800
